{"word":"G1621 - ἐκτινάσσω - ektinássō - ek-tin-as'-so - Shake","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκτινάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ektinássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-tin-as'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Shake</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உதறிப்போடு, உதறு"},{"paragraph":"to shake off, so that something adhering shall fall"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C3;&#x03C9;</b> <b>tinasso&#x0304;</b> (to <i>swing</i>); to <i>shake</i> violently: - shake (off).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}